OL,3,CUK's first Reform council leader
OL,4,Cpromises Leicestershire tax cuts
OL,6,FThe UK's first-ever Reform UK council
OL,7,Fleader said his party will be able to
OL,8,Fcut council tax as it takes aim at
OL,9,Fwasteful spending.
OL,11,FNew Leicestershire County Council
OL,12,Fleader Dan Harrison said: "To think of
OL,13,Fthe journey from where we came to
OL,14,Fwhere we are, this is just incredible."
OL,16,FThe former Conservative county
OL,17,Fcouncillor who defected to Reform UK
OL,18,Fin February, is now the party's leader
OL,19,Fin Leicestershire, and was formally
OL,20,Fconfirmed as leader on Wednesday (14
OL,21,FMay).
