OL,3,CUK's first Reform council leader
OL,4,Cpromises Leicestershire tax cuts
OL,6,FHe said: "We're now looking at the
OL,7,Fcost, the efficiency, we'll then have
OL,8,Fmoney for front line (services) but
OL,9,Fwe'll also be able to cut council tax."
OL,11,F'Something has got to change' - people
OL,12,Fin Coalville gave their feelings on
OL,13,Fthe new Reform leadership.
OL,15,FThe Conservatives lost control of the
OL,16,Fcouncil after 24 years in power, as
OL,17,FReform UK became the largest party.
OL,19,FReform UK holds 25 of Leicestershire's
OL,20,F55 seats compared to the
OL,21,FConservatives' 15.
