OL,3,CUK's first Reform council leader
OL,4,Cpromises Leicestershire tax cuts
OL,6,FNigel Farage's party won 42 of the 64
OL,7,FDerbyshire County Council seats,
OL,8,Ftaking overall control away from the
OL,9,FConservatives for the first time in
OL,10,Feight years.
OL,12,FCllr Graves said: "People will see a
OL,13,Fchange, because there'll be more
OL,14,Fpotholes sorted, the roads will be
OL,15,Fbetter, the council efficiency will
OL,16,Ffind money where it once was hidden or
OL,17,Flost and we will achieve great things."
