OL,3,CUK's first Reform council leader
OL,4,Cpromises Leicestershire tax cuts
OL,6,F"We need to make sure the council is
OL,7,Foperating properly and efficiently to
OL,8,Fsee where we can save some of the vast
OL,9,Famounts of money that is being spent."
OL,11,FHe confirmed the party's stance
OL,12,Fagainst net-zero policies, which he
OL,13,Fsaid would be streamlined to those
OL,14,Fwhich would not cost the council extra.
