OL,4,Cpromises Leicestershire tax cuts
OL,6,FAsked about how the party will tackle
OL,7,Fpotholes and SEND provision, Cllr
OL,8,FGraves said: "I've literally just been
OL,9,Felected and we have not had any
OL,10,Fdiscussions with anybody yet so give
OL,11,Fus a chance to have a chat about it
OL,12,Fand I am sure we might actually come
OL,13,Fup with something."
OL,15,FOf the 42 Reform UK councillors
OL,16,Felected in Derbyshire, none were
OL,17,Fcounty councillors before the election.
